ITEM NO.36                  COURT NO.13                  SECTION XI
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition for Special Leave to Appeal (C) No.16940/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated 01-04-2025 
in CAC No. 7355/2024 passed by the High Court of Judicature at 
Allahabad]
CHHAKKI LAL MARAL                                     Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
SRI YOGESHWAR RAM MISHRA & ORS.                       Respondent(s)
FOR ADMISSION 
 
Date : 07-07-2025 This petition was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE RAJESH BINDAL
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE R. MAHADEVAN
For Petitioner(s) : Mr. Vivek Narayan Sharma, AOR
Ms. Shruti Priya Mishra, Adv.
Ms. Mahima Bhardwaj Kalucha, Adv.
Mr. Dinesh Sharma, Adv.
                   
For Respondent(s) : 
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
No case is made out for interference with the impugned order.
The special leave petition is, accordingly, dismissed.
Pending application(s), if any, shall also stand disposed of.
(KRITIKA TIWARI)                                (SAPNA BANSAL)
SENIOR PERSONAL ASSISTANT                     COURT MASTER (NSH)
